          "instruction": "Answer the questions based on the audio.",
          "prompt_html": "<h1>MULTIPLE CHOICE 48</h1><p><strong>Questions 15 - 20</strong></p><p>Choose <strong>THREE</strong> correct answers.</p><p>Write the correct letter <strong>A - F</strong> for each answer.</p><p>Which THREE of the following are true of entry to the park?</p><p>(15)</p><p>(16)</p><p>(17)</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    Visitors must pay extra to visit the Biodome.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    Tickets for all children cost the same.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    There are reductions for visitors who are currently studying.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>D</strong>    Visitors will need to bring additional documents if they want to buy a season pass.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>E</strong>    Payment in the ticket office can only be made in cash.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>F</strong>    Visitors can withdraw cash while they are in the park.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table><p>Which THREE of the following are true of the park's attractions for children?</p><p>(18)</p><p>(19)</p><p>(20)</p><table><thead><tr><th><strong>A</strong>    All children can ride the Terrordactyl Rollercoaster.</th><th></th></tr></thead><tbody><tr><td><strong>B</strong>    There are prizes available at one of the children's attractions.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>C</strong>    It is not currently possible to go to the Cretaceous Caverns.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>D</strong>    The guide recommends the Tree Top Walk to active children.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>E</strong>    The park has facilities where younger children can be looked after.</td><td></td></tr><tr><td><strong>F</strong>    There are guided tours along the Riverside Walk.</td><td></td></tr></tbody></table>",
